excuse us. Okay?

501
00:35:49,474 --> 00:35:50,158
Hey!

502
00:35:50,183 --> 00:35:51,267
You, new girl.

503
00:35:51,267 --> 00:35:52,769
Watch your tongue.

504
00:35:52,769 --> 00:35:53,978
