Maybe I should rip that—

508
00:35:57,774 --> 00:35:58,649
Cuz, cuz, cuz.

509
00:35:58,900 --> 00:36:00,334
Just calm down. Sit first.

510
00:36:00,359 --> 00:36:01,611
Sit down, sit down.

511
00:36:02,779 --> 00:36:03,588
Let's go.

512
00:36:03,613 --> 00:36:04,030
Let's go.

513
