Yeah.

518
00:36:18,150 --> 00:36:18,920
She's just an ex-girlfriend.

519
00:36:18,920 --> 00:36:20,713
That means I should
beat her up even more.

520
00:36:21,518 --> 00:36:22,565
Come here.

521
00:36:22,590 --> 00:36:23,841
Just relax, okay?

522
00:36:24,550 --> 00:36:25,509
You know...

523
00:36:26,010 --> 00:36:27,136
She's actually nice.

524
00:36:27,136 --> 00:36:29,305
She's just a little weird.

525
00:36:29,305 --> 00:36:30,736
Sometimes she's
kind of like you.

526
00:36:32,456 --> 00:36:33,462
Me?

527
