561
00:38:23,823 --> 00:38:24,699
He's the expert.

562
00:38:24,962 --> 00:38:25,770
Yeah!

563
00:38:26,797 --> 00:38:27,607
Lerwick.

564
00:38:27,632 --> 00:38:28,364
