would cry if I died.

572
00:38:37,308 --> 00:38:38,184
Pfft!

573
00:38:38,476 --> 00:38:40,575
Coffins for sale.

574
00:38:40,853 --> 00:38:43,356
Buy one, take one.

575
00:38:44,523 --> 00:38:45,816
Hearse for rent.

576
00:38:46,609 --> 00:38:47,653
Hey!

577
00:38:47,693 --> 00:38:48,778
You guys won't teach me?

578
00:38:50,279 --> 00:38:51,822
It's not like that, Aemie.

579
00:38:52,907 --> 00:38:55,770
It would be better if Boss would be
the one to teach you.

580
00:38:56,410 --> 00:38:56,953
Right?

581
00:38:56,953 --> 00:38:57,495
Mhm.

582
00:38:58,245 --> 00:38:59,239
Let's go!

583
00:39:00,414 --> 00:39:02,083
Yay!

584
00:39:09,548 --> 00:39:10,399
Hey!

585
00:39:10,424 --> 00:39:12,541
Are all of these ours?

586
00:39:13,344 --> 00:39:14,345
Ow!

587
00:39:15,012 --> 00:39:17,682
Why'd you always have to flick my hand?

588
00:39:18,349 --> 00:39:21,185
Do not touch the
guns until I say so.

589
00:39:23,688 --> 00:39:25,064
There are many types of guns.

590
00:39:25,940 --> 00:39:28,067
But the type of gun
that's best for you,

591
00:39:28,985 --> 00:39:29,777
is this.

592
00:39:31,654 --> 00:39:33,280
Semi-automatic pistol.

593
00:39:35,741 --> 00:39:37,118
Perfect.

594
00:39:37,952 --> 00:39:39,370
Is it easy to use, Zeke?

595
00:39:40,329 --> 00:39:41,580
A beginner's a beginner.

596
00:39:42,123 --> 00:39:45,376
But there's no reason you
can't learn to shoot with this.

597
00:39:48,087 --> 00:39:49,797
I see.

598
00:39:52,049 --> 00:39:53,467
Can I have two of those?

599
00:39:54,760 --> 00:39:55,511
You know what?

600
00:39:55,511 --> 00:39:56,404
Let's go home.

601
00:39:56,429 --> 00:39:57,238
Hey!

602
00:39:57,263 --> 00:39:57,763
Why?

603
00:39:57,763 --> 00:39:59,890
We haven't even started,
and we're already going home?

604
00:40:00,057 --> 00:40:01,767
Because you talk too much.

605
00:40:02,810 --> 00:40:03,769
I was only making a suggestion.

606
00:40:03,769 --> 00:40:04,627
Shh!

607
00:40:06,147 --> 00:40:07,182
Focus.

608
00:40:07,898 --> 00:40:09,275
Can I try it now?

609
00:40:12,445 --> 00:40:13,946
Like I said, later.

610
00:40:15,906 --> 00:40:18,617
This is a semi-automatic pistol.

611
00:40:20,201 --> 00:40:22,112
The magazine holds the rounds,

612
00:40:22,621 --> 00:40:25,624
and slides easily,
quickly into the grip.

613
00:40:27,334 --> 00:40:29,003
The trigger pull is lighter,

614
00:40:29,378 --> 00:40:32,298
allowing you to fire
multiple rounds quickly.

615
00:40:39,805 --> 00:40:41,907
I like that one!

616
00:40:41,932 --> 00:40:43,142
But not too quick.

617
00:41:06,373 --> 00:41:07,541
You're amazing!

618
00:41:07,833 --> 00:41:09,168
You're amazing!

619
00:41:09,627 --> 00:41:10,628
So many!

620
00:41:13,172 --> 00:41:15,132
Me too, I want that. That many!

621
00:41:15,508 --> 00:41:17,843
Please? I also want too. It's my turn.

622
00:41:17,968 --> 00:41:19,804
I can do it.

623
00:41:19,804 --> 00:41:20,846
I'm going out for a bit.

624
00:41:21,180 --> 00:41:21,597
Go ahead.

625
00:41:21,597 --> 00:41:22,223
Wow!

626
00:41:24,058 --> 00:41:25,893
How did you become so good?

627
00:41:54,964 --> 00:41:58,425
Finally, you have the courage
to pull out your gun.

628
00:41:59,885 --> 00:42:04,473
The question is, do you
have the guts to pull the trigger,

629
00:42:04,473 --> 00:42:05,558
Nico Jeisz Young?

630
00:42:25,703 --> 00:42:27,288
I'm going to be a Mafia?

631
00:42:35,129 --> 00:42:36,297
Why are you here?

632
00:42:38,340 --> 00:42:40,217
This place looks familiar.

633
00:42:41,927 --> 00:42:44,388
And you think this place

634
00:42:44,388 --> 00:42:46,640
has answers to your questions?

635
00:42:51,729 --> 00:42:52,521
Finally.

636
00:42:53,272 --> 00:42:55,232
You have the courage to pull out your gun.

637
00:42:58,527 --> 00:42:59,945
Who are you?

638
00:43:07,036 --> 00:43:08,064
What?

639
00:43:10,456 --> 00:43:12,833
Okay, okay. Where do I go?
Where are you?

640
00:43:13,459 --> 00:43:15,252
Whether you like it or not, wife...

641
00:43:15,794 --> 00:43:16,587
life...

642
00:43:16,837 --> 00:43:18,005
is really not fair.

643
00:43:18,214 --> 00:43:19,173
If not you,

644
00:43:19,632 --> 00:43:20,716
who's behind it?

645
00:43:22,509 --> 00:43:23,403
Dead?

